Le Wagon

Le Wagon Paris Data Science Course It was a 9-week intensive coding bootcamp learning Python, Data Sourcing, Machine Learning, Data Engineering in Production and Deep Learning. I designed, implemented and shipped to production one Data Science project: Global Recall, an online tool leveraging Machine Learning algorithms in order to diagnose and predict Alzheimer disease.

Le Wagon Paris Web Dev Course It was a 9-week intensive coding bootcamp learning HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript ES2015, SQL, git, GitHub, Heroku and Ruby on Rails. I designed, implemented and shipped to production a fluffy garden manager, a magical clone of AirBnB and a Rails prototype of Storiz, an online tool designed to help writers share their ideas.
